Package gw.api.web

Class ProxiedRequestInfo

java.lang.Object
gw.api.web.ProxiedRequestInfo
public class ProxiedRequestInfo extends Object
This class will evaluate the headers used by proxies to get back to the original values. This value, once parsed (see parse(HttpServletRequest) is stored in the req so only needs to be parsed once.
